      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p>Seven <rs type="material" key="marmor">blue-grey marble</rs> fragments, H. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.16</measure>, D. <measure dim="diameter" type="length">0.20</measure> from the crowning feature of a <rs type="objectType">balustrade</rs>: the top is smooth; one side has a moulded profile, the other is smooth, tapering inwards. The underside has been left rough. Resembles <xref type="inscription" n="92" href="010012">1.12</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="94" href="010014">1.14</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="95" href="010015">1.15</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="96" href="010016">1.16</xref>. a: three joining pieces, total W. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.29</measure>; b: three joining pieces, total W. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.30</measure>; c: w. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.11</measure>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="text">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        <p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> in one line on upper fascia of moulded profile.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p><measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.025</measure>; elongated.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="date">
        <head>Date</head>
        <p><date notAfter="0600" exact="none" notBefore="0401">Fifth to sixth centuries</date> (<rs type="criteria">location</rs>, <rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p>
      </div>

      <div n="text" lang="grc" type="edition">
        <head lang="en">Edition</head>
		<div type="textpart_fragment" n="a"><ab>
		<lb n="1"/><gap dim="left" reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <w lemma="πᾶς"><supplied reason="lost">π</supplied>ᾶσιν</w> <w lemma="ὁ"><unclear reason="damage">τ</unclear>οῖς</w> <w lemma="φιλέω">φιλοῦσιν</w> <w lemma="αὐτός">αὐτ<unclear reason="damage">ὸ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied></w> <gap dim="right" reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
		</ab></div><div type="textpart_fragment" n="b"><ab><lb n="1"/><gap dim="left" reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <w lemma="βοηθέω"><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">βοήθη</supplied><unclear reason="damage">σ</unclear>ον</w> <persName type="aphrodisian" key="theodoretus1" full="yes"><name reg="Θεοδώρητος">Θεο<unclear reason="damage">δ</unclear>ωρήτῳ</name></persName> <w lemma="καί"><expan><abbr>κ</abbr><supplied reason="abbreviation">αὶ</supplied></expan></w> <persName key="Cyriacus1" type="aphrodisian" full="yes"><name reg="Κυριακός">Κυριακῷ</name></persName> <gap dim="right" reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
		</ab></div><div type="textpart_fragment" n="c"><ab><lb n="1"/><gap dim="left" reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <w lemma="ὁ">τοις</w> <w><orig n="unresolved">δια<unclear reason="damage">φ</unclear></orig><gap dim="right" reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></w>
		</ab></div>
      </div>

      <div type="translation">
        <head>Translation</head>
		<p>
		a. <gap dim="left" reason="lost"/> <supplied reason="lost">to</supplied> all that love him <gap dim="right" reason="lost"/>
		</p><p>b. <gap dim="left" reason="lost"/> <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">help</supplied> Theodoretos and Kyriakos <gap dim="right" reason="lost"/>
		</p>
      </div>

      <div type="commentary">
        <head>Commentary</head>
        <p>See discussion at <xref type="eAla-text" n="VII.10">VII.10</xref>.</p>
        
      </div>

      <div type="history" n="locations"><head>Locations</head><p>Found: <rs type="found"><rs type="monuList">Temple/Church</rs>: six fragments in sector xv, one stray find.</rs>. Original location: <rs type="origLocation"><rs type="monuList">Temple/Church</rs>: <seg cert="low">Crowning the chancel barrier</seg>.</rs>. Last recorded location: <rs type="lastLocation">Museum (1977)</rs>. </p></div>

      

      

